this week, straining Mike Johnson=E2=80=99s three-vote margin and creating =
new headaches for whips on both sides of the aisle. Yesterday, the House ho=
nored Houston Democratic Rep. Sylvester Turner, who died on Wednesday from =
=E2=80=9Cenduring health complications,=E2=80=9D according to a family stat=
ement=E2=80=94less than a year after the death of his predecessor in the 18=
